{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reopen viable coal mines & north sea gas & oil fields",
        "additional_details": "I believe Great britain is too reliant on other countrys that drill for oil & gas, all the while we have 3 once thriving industries that are sat idle, which surely would help the british economy massively",
        "background": "I want the government to open viable gas & oil fields in the north sea & also coalmines that were closed back in the 80s/90s that still have more than 20yrs worth of coal in them",
